Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's the crime scene?\N-Down those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-The victims?\N-Three males.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoroughly investigate the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we wait until Detective Kratkiy\Narrives before doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of this investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find anyone suspicious,\Ndetain them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But what kind of people would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who seems suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't take orders\Njust because I'm a rookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Suk of the Prague Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty brutal scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zeman…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was beaten to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even recognize his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If his police ID hadn't fallen out,\NI doubt we could've identified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,PRAGUE CITY POLICE\NFILIP ZEMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two other male corpses\Nover there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't identified them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One was shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was beaten to death\Nlike Inspector Zeman was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Preserve the murder scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't found anyone suspicious…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They make fun of me\Njust because I'm a rookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those damned uniformed officers\Nwon't even take orders from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to listen\Nto a guy they can't respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You threw up at the scene, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to take orders\Nfrom a pathetic detective like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because\Nyou love watching detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you can do the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan's always gotten carried away,\Neven when we were in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how well Inspector Zeman\Ntreated me, but now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started,\NI didn't know how to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but Inspector Zeman taught me\Nhow to be a real detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I respected\NInspector Zeman with all my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll avenge\NInspector Zeman's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find his murderer\Neven if I have to do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well…\N-We've got work early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?\NHang out with me longer, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole reason\Nyou can live and work safely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I'm fighting for justice,\Nyou know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here! Drink up!\N-Cut that out, would you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we work\Nevery single day to preserve justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we just end up getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the woman from the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spotted her twice\Nat the supermarket I dropped by
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,after working the night shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to her,\Nbut I couldn't bring myself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I found her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A hottie like her will never talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jan Suk.\NI'm not some creep or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it,\Nbut I'm a police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't let that frighten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off duty now. This is my private time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably pointless…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we may as well give him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pal's pretty depressed today.\NCan you let him chat with you for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something terrible happened to\Na respected superior of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been crying his eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never known anyone as kind as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become like Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll get his murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll catch them…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm doing all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You must do your best to catch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the murderer for that inspector's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you a lot about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't said\Na word about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know… my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got an idea.\NI'll guess what your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective, after all.\NLeave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, your name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know myself,\Nso there's no way you could know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only things I know about myself are…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cedok Bridge and three frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you it was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's way out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've identified the other two men\Nwho were killed with Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One is Chesmir Marat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is Yakov Suachek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They were both sergeants of\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After the fall of socialism,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they did dirty work\Nexclusively for underground organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood stains\Nat the murder scene have been analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood from someone other than\NInspector Zeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marat and Suachek has been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood type is AB+.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the amount of blood found,\Nit's presumed they're severely injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working to identify\Nwho it belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring out the window for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're desperately searching\Nfor whoever murdered a gifted colleague,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like it was mentioned at the top,\Na witness said they saw a man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,walking near the murder scene\Njust after it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a tall and slim man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked like a tourist\Ncarrying a large bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to do everything\Nyou can to track this man down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no way she'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the person\Nwho murdered your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pathetic to think\Nthat they're out there roaming free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zeman was up all night\Nthe day before investigating a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What murder was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An old man who was operating\Nan unlicensed orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and his maid were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, he questioned\Nthe person who first found the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the person\Nwho first found the bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see. He seemed like a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was tall and thin,\Nand was carrying a really heavy bag…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thin… tall… carrying a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can find out.\NI'll call the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck, Mister Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cedok Bridge and three frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cedok Bridge. That's in\Nthe old part of town in Michalska.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I come here, I can find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's checked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer checked out\Nin the morning two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who murdered Inspector Zeman is\Nthe man who stayed in this room, Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! How come I didn't realize\Nit was him sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zeman, I'll catch this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ask you the same thing,\NChief Detective Patera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you were able\Nto figure all this out on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be the first to break\Nthe murder case of Inspector Zeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I see you've already\Ngotten this far as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you still did break the case.\NNicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'd like you to keep\Nthis whole thing under wraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How come? Shouldn't we be working\Nas fast as we can to catch Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This case\Nis a little more complex than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know about the top-secret\Ninvestigation Inspector Zeman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was entrusted with, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was working on\Na top-secret investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He was identifying members\Nof the former Czechoslovakia secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who falsified their records\Nand are working with the Prague Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Czechoslovakia secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The two other murdered men were\Nalso former secret police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Only me, the chief,\Nand a few others know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dig too deep into this,\Nyou'll be killed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet about this, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see. Grimmer might just\Nshow up at this hotel again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stake out this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Suk. Do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, you were daydreaming\Nat your desk this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She just happens to come\Nto the bar I always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a hottie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you introduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's this bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Introduce you?\NI don't think I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said she's not your girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk won't be here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, what a surprise. You are a hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Suk's superior. My name's Patera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me he knows\Na really beautiful woman at this bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on a stakeout tonight,\Nso he won't be coming by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not have a drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one little drink won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Detective Janáček. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Patera told me that chick\Nyou've got your eye on is a real hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You went to that bar, Mr. Patera?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you hit on her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Suk. Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chief Detective Patera is\Nknown for really having a way with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. She gave me\Nthe cold shoulder pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If even Mr. Patera couldn't get her,\Nthen she must be a pretty tough cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply like her\Nbecause she's nice to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Farobek wants you to go\Nto Inspector Zeman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given these. Want a whiskey bonbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want one, Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep what you know about\Nthat tall suspect under wraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pretty much cleaned out\NInspector Zeman's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left are his personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pack those things up\Nand take them to his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the key to a gym locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! This stinks terribly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bunch of sweaty t-shirts\Nand towels here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a file of detailed personnel records\Nof everyone in the Prague Police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even mine's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know about the top-secret\Ninvestigation Inspector Zeman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was entrusted with, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He was identifying members\Nof the former Czechoslovakia secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who falsified their records\Nand are working in the Prague Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How come there's no record of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Detective Patera\Nor Detective Janáček?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is\Nan extraordinarily large amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk, what do you surmise\Nfrom these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I believe Inspector Zeman was\Ncarrying out an internal investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He discovered that Chief Detective Patera\Nand Detective Janáček were
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,members of the former\NCzechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to say this, but I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that Inspector Zeman took a bribe\Nto keep quiet about what he discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very grave problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,\NI want to keep this under wraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you later.\NFor now, return to your regular duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain this has turned out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to underestimate\Nwhat a greenhorn like Suk could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't found\Nthat tall guy who murdered Zeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but now we've got another problem\Non our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to solve this with money\Nlike we did with Zeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that doesn't work,\Nwe've only got one other option, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,since I let you join the police\Nwith full knowledge of your past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to make certain\Nthis doesn't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to cover this up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use a drink about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I got whiskey bonbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a present from that hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? You look depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You can tell me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all people, I was sure\Nthat Inspector Zeman wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,\Nthe only person that I can trust…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is you.
